Package mars.assembler

Class Symbol

java.lang.Object
mars.assembler.Symbol
public class Symbol extends Object
Represents a MIPS program identifier to be stored in the symbol table.
Version:
June 2003
Author:
Jason Bumgarner, Jason Shrewsbury
